{"word":"G4256 - προαιτιάομαι - proaitiáomai - pro-ahee-tee-ah'-om-ahee - Prove before","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προαιτιάομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">proaitiáomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pro-ahee-tee-ah'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Prove before</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நியமித்தபடியே கொடு"},{"paragraph":"to bring a charge against previously"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4253 - πρό - pró - pro/4253\">G4253</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G156 - αἰτία - aitía - ahee-tee'-a/156\">G156</a>; to <i>accuse already</i>, that is, <i>previously charge:</i> - prove before.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}